      h1 Unlocking Creativity with OpenAI Sora
      h2.subheading.mb-3 Revolutionizing AI-Driven Video Generation
      p.
        This morning, I saw the 'Sora' icon on my ChatGPT Pro subscription
        and had the happy experience of diving into its text-to-video capabilities.
        After experimenting with a few prompts to generate videos,
        I decided to write this article to share my initial results and provide an overview of the tool.
        The interface was intuitive, and the options straightforward,
        making it easy for me to start creating.
        For me, Sora feels more like a novelty and a glimpse into better things to come than a complete revolution.
        However, it offers something I couldn't do before: the ability to create small video clips quickly and efficiently.
      p.
